snippet.title: The Haunting | Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II & Warzone
snippet.description:
Season 06 just got a lot spookier 👻 

Face your fears in The Haunting when the Limited-Time Mode drops in Call of Duty #Warzone and #MWII on October 17 💀
